<A>__{to wide shot of massive imposing lobby much like the records lobby but this one is very austere. no crowds. no statues. no decoration. not even the ever present security checks. impressive. and a bit unnerving. framed in the doorway is a lone tiny figure. cut : to close up. it's sam. he hesitates and then enters. cut : to video screen. the video camera follows sam across the lobby til he stops in tight profile at reception desk. we tilt up revealing sam standing facing us just beyond the monitor which is on the desk.}
